Add Media remote indicators for Improved mode and mouse switcher

The Media view now reflects its active settings: the title shows
"Media+" when Improved mode is on, and the dpad Back button shows a
mouse icon (instead of the back-arrow) when the Mouse Switcher is
enabled, signaling that tapping Back opens the mouse sub-view.

Both flags are pushed into the view model via a new hid_media_set_mode()
setter, called on entry from the Start scene like hid_keynote_set_orientation.

